    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "##  🔍Teacher Tip\r\nCheck out the **system prompt** for this chatbot.\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; background-color: #F5F7F8; padding: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #8148B2; display: inline-block;\">\r\n    ➡️ This activity is from Lesson 2. You can find more details in the full <a href='https://studio.code.org' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer' style='text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;'>Lesson Plan</a>.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Driving Chatbot\r\n\r\n### Do This\r\n\r\n1) **Predict:** What do you notice? What do you wonder? How do you expect the chatbot to respond?\r\n2) **Investigate:** Test the chatbot with at least 4 different messages\r\n3) **Reflect:** What worked like you expected? What surprised you?\r\n\r\nOnce you're finished, press the <code style=\"color:white; background-color:#7435b2\">Continue</code> button!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n::: details [**Click here to see example messages to try in this level**]\r\n* What are the requirements to get a driving permit?\r\n* What happens if you run a red light?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n&nbsp;",
